Implement infinite carousel for ProjectGallery component

- Added infinite scrolling functionality with duplicated items array
- Implemented smooth auto-scroll with configurable interval and pause on hover
- Added touch/drag support for manual navigation
- Enhanced loading states with skeleton placeholders
- Improved image handling with fixed dimensions (300x240) for consistency
- Added glassmorphism overlay effects and zoom indicators
- Optimized performance with proper cleanup and event handlers
- Maintained responsive design and accessibility features

Changes include:
- New infiniteItems computed property for seamless looping
- Auto-scroll mechanism with user interaction detection
- Enhanced motion variants and animations
- Improved error handling and loading states
- Better UX with hover effects and visual feedback
